title: Truckfighters Discography
description:
2005 - Gravity X
2007 - Phi
2009 - Mania

Bonus:
2003 - Fuzzsplit of the Century: Truckfighters vs. Firestone

Gathered these from other trackers.  Gravity and Phi were together.  The others were seperate.  Mania was a single FLAC paired with a CUE.  I split the tracks using CUETools.
Properly repackaged, renamed, re-tagged, and sorted.

Sounds excellent played at high volumes through large, good speakers.  
I had to include the Fuzzsplit.  Some of those tracks are just amazing.  Listen to New Woman.  It is an ass puncher for sure.

If you enjoy, please buy their merch and go to a show.
